        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-number">02</div><div class="training-card-title">Discipline.</div><div class="training-card-desc">Repeated adherence to the standard when motivation is no longer enough.</div></div>
        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-number">03</div><div class="training-card-title">Execution.</div><div class="training-card-desc">Intent must translate into measurable action, precision, and completed work.</div></div>
        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-number">04</div><div class="training-card-title">Performance Systems.</div><div class="training-card-desc">Structured protocols designed to create durable, accountable progress.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-warm-gray);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-warm-gray);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <div class="text-eyebrow mb-sm">Performance Systems</div>
          <h2 class="text-h2">Programs built for athletes who train with intent.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="services-list" style="border-top:none;">
        <div class="service-row"><div><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">01 / PROTOCOL</div><div class="service-name">Protocol — Threshold</div></div><div class="service-desc">Advanced performance development emphasizing neural efficiency, force production, and high-intensity execution. Built for athletes operating above baseline standards and seeking elevated output within a controlled training environment.</div><div class="service-arrow"><a href="/pages/contact">Apply for Threshold</a></div></div>
        <div class="service-row"><div><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">02 / PROTOCOL</div><div class="service-name">Protocol — Capacity</div></div><div class="service-desc">Structured performance training built on volume architecture, strength progression, and metabolic control. Designed for athletes and professionals seeking consistent output, measurable progression, and disciplined execution inside the AREN system.</div><div class="service-arrow"><a href="/pages/contact">Enter Capacity</a></div></div>
        <div class="service-row"><div><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">03 / COLLECTIVE</div><div class="service-name">National Collective</div></div><div class="service-desc">Open-format performance movement unified under shared standards. Community-driven sessions built around exploration, discipline, and collective execution across boroughs.</div><div class="service-arrow"><a href="/pages/street-miles">Join Street Miles</a></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.2fr) minmax(0,.8fr);gap:var(--space-xl);align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <div class="text-eyebrow mb-sm">Who Trains With Intent?</div>
        <h2 class="text-h2" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">The standard is not for everyone.</h2>
        <ul class="text-body" style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:grid;gap:1rem;">
          <li>— Individuals who prioritize performance output over public opinion.</li>
          <li>— Athletes committed to consistent physiological execution and accountability.</li>
          <li>— Performers who maintain operational composure under high-stress thresholds.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="training-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1rem;">
        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-number">100%</div><div class="training-card-title">Execution</div></div>
        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-number">HIGH</div><div class="training-card-title">Composure</div></div>
        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-number">STRICT</div><div class="training-card-title">Adherence</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--color-off-white);border-top:1px solid var(--color-warm-gray);">
    <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,.9fr) minmax(0,1.1fr);gap:var(--space-xl);align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <div class="text-eyebrow mb-sm">Get Started</div>
        <h2 class="text-h2" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Execute the first step.</h2>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Response Protocol: 24h. We respond to all serious inquiries within 24 hours.</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><a href="mailto:{{ settings.email_address | default: 'info@arenathletic.com' }}">{{ settings.email_address | default: 'info@arenathletic.com' }}</a></p>
        <p class="text-body">37 Union Sq West, 2nd Floor, New York, NY 10003</p>
      </div>
      <div>{% form 'contact', id: 'training-contact-form', class: 'contact-form' %}<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;"><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="TrainingFirstName">First Name *</label><input class="form-input" type="text" id="TrainingFirstName" name="contact[first_name]" required></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="TrainingLastName">Last Name *</label><input class="form-input" type="text" id="TrainingLastName" name="contact[last_name]" required></div></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="TrainingEmail">Email *</label><input class="form-input" type="email" id="TrainingEmail" name="contact[email]" required></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="TrainingPhone">Phone</label><input class="form-input" type="tel" id="TrainingPhone" name="contact[phone]"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="TrainingReferral">Referral Source</label><input class="form-input" type="text" id="TrainingReferral" name="contact[referral_source]"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="TrainingWhy">Why are you looking to train? *</label><textarea class="form-textarea" id="TrainingWhy" name="contact[body]" required></textarea></div><button class="btn btn--primary" type="submit">Submit</button><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-top:1rem;">Response Protocol: 24h</div>{% if form.posted_successfully? %}<div id="training-contact-success" class="text-eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-top:1rem;">Received.<br>We'll be in touch within 24 hours.</div>{% endif %}{{ form.errors | default_errors }}{% endform %}</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% if page.content != blank %}<section class="section"><div class="container rte">{{ page.content }}</div></section>{% endif %}

