        <div class="service-row"><div><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">01 / SESSIONS</div><div class="service-name">Structure</div></div><div class="service-desc">Every Sunday at 09:00 sharp. We execute rotating sessions across the five boroughs—focused on bridges, blocks, and industrial sectors.</div></div>
