        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-desc">"Street Miles is the street-level expression of AREN's standards. We forge mental and physical resilience through shared miles and collective accountability. We do the work; we carry the weight."</div><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-top:1rem;">ATHLETE 089 / SMNYC CHAPTER</div></div>
        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-desc">"This is not a social run club. It is a disciplined ecosystem for athletes who show up regardless of conditions, where presence is the metric and repetition is the method."</div><div class="text-eyebrow" style="margin-top:1rem;">ATHLETE 042 / SMNYC CHAPTER</div></div>
